Who are you?

334
00:27:51.016 --> 00:27:53.007
Robert Loxley.

335
00:28:13.772 --> 00:28:15.740
That's the King's horse.

336
00:28:20.812 --> 00:28:22.746
<font color="#ff80ff">WILL:</font> Jimmy! Move!

337
00:28:33.225 --> 00:28:35.651
Jimmy!

338
00:28:47.372 --> 00:28:48.930
<font color="#ff80ff">ALLAN:</font> Robin, they're French.

339
00:28:49.007 --> 00:28:50.201
Ambush.

340
00:29:08.760 --> 00:29:09.852
Go.

341
00:29:09.961 --> 00:29:12.058
<font color="#ff80ff">(ROARING)</font>

342
00:29:47.766 --> 00:29:49.658
John.

343
00:29:50.235 --> 00:29:51.461
Don't know.

344
00:29:51.536 --> 00:29:53.067
He's dead.

345
00:29:53.071 --> 00:29:54.163
Help.

346
00:30:02.914 --> 00:30:04.176
My sword.

347
00:30:14.493 --> 00:30:16.984
Its value to me is great.

348
00:30:17.762 --> 00:30:20.330
It belonged to my father,

349
00:30:20.999 --> 00:30:22.159
Sir Walter Loxley

350
00:30:23.401 --> 00:30:24.891
