488
00:41:08.379 --> 00:41:09.744
Part for the Queen.

489
00:41:34.739 --> 00:41:35.899
Cease.

490
00:41:57.695 --> 00:41:59.287
What's this? What's happening?

491
00:41:59.363 --> 00:42:01.558
King Richard returns from France,
My Lord.

492
00:42:06.337 --> 00:42:08.202
